No.

576
00:32:51,910 --> 00:32:53,781
Dentro de un rato
se va a servir la cena.

577
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:55,080
No voy a cenar.

578
00:32:57,340 --> 00:32:58,340
Con permiso.

